NK033(gi)005:1: // klong sde rdo rje zam pa las sgom tshul bla
NK033(gi)005:2: ma'i byin rlabs rgyas pa'i chog khrigs su bkod pa
NK033(gi)005:3: ye shes chu rgyun zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)005:4: na mo gu ru sh+r+ai he ru ka ya /
NK033(gi)005:5: brda' dang tshul bzhi'i gnad kyis dus thung ngur //
NK033(gi)005:6: 'od skur grol byed mchog gsang a ti'i lam //
NK033(gi)005:7: ston mdzad rig 'dzin rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK033(gi)005:8: dpal chen mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)005:9: smin byed thabs tshul rgyas bsdus ji snyed pas //
NK033(gi)005:10: nam yang mi bskrun brda thabs byin rlabs kyis //
NK033(gi)005:11: dbang rnon skad cig grol byed rdzogs pa che'i //
NK033(gi)005:12: bka' srol bdud rtsi'i yang zhun btung bar byos //
NK033(gi)005:13: klong sde sna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i rnal 'byor
NK033(gi)005:14: du bya ba'i rim pa gsum pa smin pa grol
NK033(gi)005:15: bar byed pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi
NK033(gi)005:16: cho ga rgyas par bya ba la don gsum /
NK033(gi)005:20: dang po dkyil 'khor dang rdzas bshams pa ni /
NK033(gi)005:21: stegs gtsang ma'i steng bdud rtsi lngas chag chag btab pa la /
NK033(gi)005:22: lte ba zlum skor rim pa lnga bskor ba'i dbus mthing ga /
NK033(gi)005:27: de'i phyi la chos 'byung bsnol ma'i steng dmar po /
NK033(gi)005:30: chos 'byung zur drug gi rtse mor rdo rje ser
NK033(gi)005:31: po bri ba'ang yod pas de ltar na chos 'byung
NK033(gi)005:32: gi phyi la zlum skor yangs pa bya /
NK033(gi)005:33: de rgyab zlum skor rim par gsum gyi dang po nyi dkyil dmar /
NK033(gi)005:35: gsum pa sna tshogs pad+ma bri /
NK033(gi)005:36: de rgyab gru bzhi rim pa gnyis bcad pa'i nang ma shar dkar /
NK033(gi)005:40: de rgyab mu ran shar dmar /
NK033(gi)005:43: byang mthing ga can gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs /
NK033(gi)005:44: de'i dbus su khri'u la 'bru yis bkang ba'i snod
NK033(gi)005:45: du rin po che'i bum pa dri bzang chu dang
NK033(gi)005:46: nyer lnga'i rdzas kyis bkang ba la mgul chings kha
NK033(gi)005:47: dog lnga ldan gu gul gyis bdug /
NK033(gi)005:48: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad la bzhag /
NK033(gi)005:49: de'i steng ka p+aa la dum bu gcig pa'i nang
NK033(gi)005:50: sin+d+hu ras byugs pa la chos 'byung bsnol ma'i lte
NK033(gi)005:52: +aaham h'u h+r+aihb+h+r+aum ham zhes pa'i 'bru drug mgo nang
NK033(gi)005:53: bstan du bris pa'i nang chang dang chos sman sbyar
NK033(gi)005:54: bas bkang ba'i khar me long sin+d+hu ra brdal ba
NK033(gi)005:55: la / chos 'byung sngags bcad snga ma ltar bris
NK033(gi)005:56: pas bkab pa'i steng byang sems dkar dmar gyi ril
NK033(gi)005:57: bu bzhag la dar dkar dmar gyis dgab /
NK033(gi)005:65: ka ra rnams cha mnyam sbyar ba dkar po dang /
NK033(gi)005:69: pad rag sogs rin po che dmar po /
NK033(gi)005:71: bu ram rnams sbyar ba dmar po ste gnyis ka
NK033(gi)005:72: mar gyis ril bur bsgril ba slob ma'i grangs mnyam
NK033(gi)005:73: byas la / dkar po dar dkar dang de rgyab dar dmar gyis dril /
NK033(gi)005:74: dmar po dar dmar dang de rgyab dkar pos dril la bzhag /
NK033(gi)005:76: bla ma dang yi dam gyi gtor ma /
NK033(gi)005:77: mkha' 'gro la gtor ma gsum sha khrag /
NK033(gi)005:79: dkar mngar gyis brgyan pa'am las byang du bshad pa ltar dang /
NK033(gi)005:82: zhun chen gyi mar me mtshan thub gsum /
NK033(gi)005:83: nye spyod lnga rnams kyis mtha' bskor /
NK033(gi)005:86: rdo rje'i tshig rkang bris pa'i tshul shing /
NK033(gi)005:92: mchod gtor sogs nyer mkho rnams tshogs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)005:93: byin 'bebs kyi dus su mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i
NK033(gi)005:94: spos sbyor gal che bas gzhung du 'byung ba ltar
NK033(gi)005:96: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis /
NK033(gi)005:100: las byang gi dbur bkod pa ltar phyi nang gi rgya mtsho khrus lung dang /
NK033(gi)005:101: sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa sngon du btang la /
NK033(gi)005:102: man+dala gyi dbus su gu ser po /
NK033(gi)005:105: de'i steng du pam yig kha dog lnga pa /
NK033(gi)005:114: de dag gi dbus su chos 'byung bsnol ma dmar po /
NK033(gi)005:115: de'i nang du ba mthing ga /
NK033(gi)005:118: de'i steng ba ti dmar po /
NK033(gi)005:123: sna tshogs pad+ma'i gdan ge sar dang bcas pa de dag gi shar phyogs su ke dkar po /
NK033(gi)005:125: ke ru dkar po'i zhing khams /
NK033(gi)005:126: lho phyogs su bee mthing ga /
NK033(gi)005:127: bee d+aur+ya man+dala sngon po'i zhing khams nub phyogs su pam dmar po /
NK033(gi)005:129: pad rag dmar po'i zhing khams /
NK033(gi)005:130: byang phyogs su in+d+ra n+ai ljang gu /
NK033(gi)005:132: in+d+ra n+ai la ljang gu'i zhing khams su gyur /
NK033(gi)005:133: gnyis pa rdzas byin gyis brlab pa la gsum las bum pa byin rlabs ni /
NK033(gi)005:134: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi pad+ma ge sar gyi steng du
NK033(gi)005:135: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs
NK033(gi)005:136: pa'i nang du +amo yig kha dog lnga ldan /
NK033(gi)005:141: 'a ljang gur yod pa de las 'od zer sna
NK033(gi)005:142: lnga 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK033(gi)005:144: sku'i byin rlabs thams cad 'od zer gyi rnam par
NK033(gi)005:145: dbu'i gtsug tor las thon nas bum pa'i nang du
NK033(gi)005:146: thim par bsam / +amo sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK033(gi)005:147: he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru
NK033(gi)005:148: lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)005:151: ka p+aa la yi nang du +aahdamara ser gcig gsal /
NK033(gi)005:152: de las 'od zer sna lnga 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i
NK033(gi)005:153: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul
NK033(gi)005:154: / gsung gi byin rlabs thams cad 'od zer gyi
NK033(gi)005:155: rnam par ljags kyi dbang po las thon nas ka
NK033(gi)005:156: p+aa la'i nang du thim pa bsam /
NK033(gi)005:157: +amo +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)005:160: me long gi nang du ham dkar po zhig gsal /
NK033(gi)005:161: de las 'od zer sna lnga 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i
NK033(gi)005:162: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul
NK033(gi)005:163: / thugs kyi byin rlabs thams cad 'od zer gyi
NK033(gi)005:164: rnam pa thugs ka nas thon te me long gi
NK033(gi)005:171: dang po ni las byang gi bgegs bsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)005:172: brgyud 'debs nas brtsam mthar chags su btang /
NK033(gi)005:173: dkyil 'khor bdag mdun dbyer med snang srid gzhir bzhengs su bskyed /
NK033(gi)005:174: gzhung gi bzlas pa grub nas /
NK033(gi)005:175: sku gsung thugs kyi he ru ka gsum gyi snying po gong gsal so sor /
NK033(gi)005:176: +amo +amo a a sarba ta th+aa ga ta ya h'u /
NK033(gi)005:177: +amo +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)005:178: zhes btags pa ci nus bzla zhing byin rlabs bsdu ba'i dmigs pa bya /
NK033(gi)005:179: tshe bum tshe dpag med du gsal ba las spro bsdu spyi ltar byas la /
NK033(gi)005:186: tshogs mchod lhag ma yan chad grub par bya /
NK033(gi)005:187: gdod nas 'khor 'das thams cad kun tu bzang mo'i
NK033(gi)005:188: klong chen gcig tu rdzogs pa'i lta ba'i gdeng bskyed
NK033(gi)005:189: pa las spros bcas kyi bdag 'jug mi dgos so
NK033(gi)005:190: // gnyis pa byin rlabs kyi cho ga la spyi
NK033(gi)005:191: don bco lngar bshad pa'i dang po rgyud sbyong ba
NK033(gi)005:192: // ni / khrus kyi bum pas slob ma rnams phyi rol tu khrus bya /
NK033(gi)005:193: bgegs bskrad cing nang du zhugs nas srung 'khor bsgom /
NK033(gi)005:194: skyabs 'gro dang khyad par sems bskyed kyi sdom pa
NK033(gi)005:195: sngon du ma thob pa yin na skyabs sems sdom
NK033(gi)005:196: chog lugs 'dir zur du 'byung ba nyid gal che
NK033(gi)005:198: de dag thob zin pa la skabs 'dir mdor bsdus tsam bya ste /
NK033(gi)005:199: de la khyed rang rnams theg pa chen po'i yang
NK033(gi)005:200: rtse bla na med pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa
NK033(gi)005:201: la dang po thun mong gi lam du rgyud sbyong
NK033(gi)005:203: mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK033(gi)005:204: tshogs rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa mngon sum bzhin
NK033(gi)005:205: du bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar bdag gzhan mkha' khyab kyi
NK033(gi)005:206: sems can thams cad snying po byang chub la mchis
NK033(gi)005:207: kyi bar du skyabs su mchi'o snyam pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:208: rgyun bshags yan lag brgyad pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams re re bzhin gsal 'debs shing /
NK033(gi)005:209: smon pa dang 'jug pa'i bsam sbyor phun sum tshogs
NK033(gi)005:210: pa dang ldan pas 'di rnams kyi rjes zlos mdzod
NK033(gi)005:212: rdo rje slob dpon sogs nas /
NK033(gi)005:214: bar lan gsum brjod du gzhug /
NK033(gi)005:215: gnyis pa gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK033(gi)005:216: ras sam snam dkar gyi gdan la me tog gi tshom bu lnga bkod /
NK033(gi)005:217: lag tu rdo rje 'jur bcug la /
NK033(gi)005:218: de ltar rgyud rnam par dag par byas pa'i slob
NK033(gi)005:219: ma nyid gnyis pa dbang stegs kyi gdan la bzhag
NK033(gi)005:220: par mos shig / 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste /
NK033(gi)005:221: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol //
NK033(gi)005:222: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK033(gi)005:223: chos dang chos nyid bsgom par gyis //
NK033(gi)005:224: zhes pas gdan la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)005:225: gsum pa rdo rje rtse mo'i dkyil 'khor gnyan por
NK033(gi)005:226: zhugs phyin chad dam tshig gi gnas las 'das na
NK033(gi)005:227: phung bar 'gyur cing srung na dngos grub mtha' dag
NK033(gi)005:228: 'thob par 'gyur bas dpang po'i tshul du mna' chu
NK033(gi)005:229: sbyin pa'i don nges par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)005:232: 'di ni rdo rje dmyal ba'i chu //
NK033(gi)005:233: dam tshig nyams na sregs par byed //
NK033(gi)005:234: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ster //
NK033(gi)005:236: +amo badz+ra a mri ta ha na ha na h'u /
NK033(gi)005:238: bzhi pa rgyud la ye shes bskyed par bya ba lags te /
NK033(gi)005:239: ye shes 'di ni ye shes che //
NK033(gi)005:240: ye shes dam pa yod med shes //
NK033(gi)005:241: ye shes ye shes khyad par shes //
NK033(gi)005:242: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)005:244: de nas sems bskyed gsal gdab cing lo rgyus mdor bsdus spro na /
NK033(gi)005:245: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)005:246: don du rigs kun khyab bdag kun bzang gdod ma'i
NK033(gi)005:248: de'i ched du dpal mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor
NK033(gi)005:249: du zhugs shing lam zab mo nyams su blang bar
NK033(gi)005:250: bagyi'o snyam pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa
NK033(gi)005:251: gsal thob la gsan par zhu /
NK033(gi)005:252: de la gsan bya dam pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK033(gi)005:253: mtha' yas pa zhig mchis pa las skabs su babs
NK033(gi)005:254: pa 'di ni snga 'gyur rnying ma'i bka' srol la
NK033(gi)005:255: theg pa rim pa dgur grags pa rnams kyi nang
NK033(gi)005:256: nas mchog tu gyur pa nang dbang bsgyur thabs kyi
NK033(gi)005:257: theg pa / de la'ang thabs dang shes rab dang
NK033(gi)005:258: zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor gtsor bton pa'i dbang las
NK033(gi)005:259: ma h+aa a nu a ti ste yo ga rnam
NK033(gi)005:260: pa gsum las 'dir thams cad kyi yang rtse a
NK033(gi)005:261: theg pa / ti yo ga / de la'ang phyi sems sde /
NK033(gi)005:263: gsang ba man ngag gi sde dang gsum du bzhugs
NK033(gi)005:264: pa las 'dir chos thams cad chos nyid kun tu
NK033(gi)005:265: bzang mo'i klong las nam yang 'dar med pa ston
NK033(gi)005:267: 'di la rgyud lung man ngag gi rim pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa bzhugs shing /
NK033(gi)005:268: de dag las phal mo che zhig 'ja' lus rdo
NK033(gi)005:269: rje'i sku brnyes pa rig 'dzin grub pa yongs kyi
NK033(gi)005:270: gtsug rgyan slob dpon chen po sh+r+ai sed+ha las /
NK033(gi)005:271: rnam snang sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po bee
NK033(gi)005:272: ro tsa nas dka' ba mang du spyad nas gsan
NK033(gi)005:273: te klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud la sogs
NK033(gi)005:275: lo ts+aa ba nyid kyang 'ja' lus kyi grub mthar
NK033(gi)005:276: gshegs shing gdams ngag spang mi pham mgon po la
NK033(gi)005:277: chig brgyud du gnang bas des mtshon rgyud pa lnga'i
NK033(gi)005:278: bar du 'ja' lus su gshegs pa sha stag byung
NK033(gi)005:279: / de las kyang gdod ma'i btsan sa zin pa'i
NK033(gi)005:280: grub thob kyi brgyud pa bar ma chad pa las
NK033(gi)005:281: byon pa'i rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa las dbang
NK033(gi)005:282: gi cho ga rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum du bzhugs pa
NK033(gi)005:283: las sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs su grags pa'i
NK033(gi)005:284: cho ga rgyas pa bgyi ba la bdag nyid kyi
NK033(gi)005:285: bgyi bar 'os pa rnams ma tshang ba med pa
NK033(gi)005:286: / grub zin / khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal
NK033(gi)005:287: du gyur pa dbang bskur zhu ba'i yon du dmigs
NK033(gi)005:290: lnga pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)005:291: slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang dbyer ma
NK033(gi)005:292: mchis pa la mi phyed dad pa'i gdung shugs drag
NK033(gi)005:293: pos thal mo me tog dang bcas te 'di'i rjes
NK033(gi)005:294: zlos / slob dpon dag ni dpal chen po //
NK033(gi)005:295: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK033(gi)005:297: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)005:298: bdag ni tshul chen snod yin te //
NK033(gi)005:299: zhes gsol ba lan gsum du gdab bo //
NK033(gi)005:300: drug pa gnang ba stsal zhing skal pa 'dri ba lags te /
NK033(gi)005:301: rigs kyi bu khyod gang la dga' //
NK033(gi)005:302: zhes pa'i lan gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK033(gi)005:303: bdag ni bde ba chen po'i skal bzang la dga' /
NK033(gi)005:305: bdun pa las kyi rdo rje'i phyag gi rdo rje
NK033(gi)005:306: la bzung ste dkyil 'khor gyi nang du gzhug par
NK033(gi)005:307: mos shig / rdo rjee lag tu 'jur bcug la /
NK033(gi)005:308: bu 'dir shog cig theg chen don //
NK033(gi)005:309: khyod la yang dag bstan par bya //
NK033(gi)005:310: dkyil 'khor chen po la gnas pa'i //
NK033(gi)005:311: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK033(gi)005:312: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)005:313: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)005:315: brgyad pa rdo rje'i dam tshig 'bog pa lags pas 'di lags gsan 'tshal /
NK033(gi)005:316: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK033(gi)005:317: bsgom bya lha dang sgom byed mi //
NK033(gi)005:318: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK033(gi)005:319: dang po rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK033(gi)005:320: lus kyi lha dang ngag gi sngags //
NK033(gi)005:321: yid kyi brda la blta ba'o //
NK033(gi)005:322: gnyis pa la ni rnam pa gsum //
NK033(gi)005:323: seng ge dkar mo'i sha mi za //
NK033(gi)005:324: za ma tog tu dug mi btso //
NK033(gi)005:325: gnam lcags dur mo'i kha mi brdab //
NK033(gi)005:327: de'ang spyir theg pa'i rtse rgyal 'dir 'jug la bslab pa'i mtha' drug dang ldan par dgos te /
NK033(gi)005:331: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang /
NK033(gi)005:333: don man ngag gis bsgrub pa rnams tshang dgos pa lags //
NK033(gi)005:334: de la thog mar thams cad kyi gzhi dang rtsa
NK033(gi)005:335: bar gyur pa dam tshig la'ang spros na rgya che'ang
NK033(gi)005:336: / 'dir man ngag gi rim pas mdor bsdus te /
NK033(gi)005:337: bsgom bya lha'i ngos nas bzhag pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:338: sgom byed mi'i ngos nas bzhag pa gnyis su bstan /
NK033(gi)005:339: dang po la lus kyis lha bar ma chad par bsgom pa mtshan ma dbyibs kyi rnal 'byor /
NK033(gi)005:340: ngag gis sngags rgyun chad med par bzla ba 'phro ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor /
NK033(gi)005:341: yid kyis brda bzhi'i gnad yengs med du sgom pa
NK033(gi)005:342: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor te sku gsum
NK033(gi)005:343: gyi rnal 'byor la yod pa snying rje'i dam tshig
NK033(gi)005:344: dang med pa chos nyid kyi dam tshig gnyis kyang
NK033(gi)005:345: 'du ba yin / gnyis pa la rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK033(gi)005:346: las mdor bsdus pa'i dam tshig nyi shu tham pa
NK033(gi)005:347: nyid gtso bo gsum du bsdu ba ste /
NK033(gi)005:348: rdo rje slob dpon la lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK033(gi)005:349: sgo nas ma gus pa skad cig mi bya zhing
NK033(gi)005:350: sgo gsum gyi mnyes pas sgrub pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:351: slob dpon gyi yum la mi spyad pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:352: rnal 'byor pa mched lcam nang 'thab mi byed pa
NK033(gi)005:353: ste rtsa ba gsum la yan lag bcu bdun pa
NK033(gi)005:354: rnams kyang blang dor phyed par byas nas bsrung mtshams
NK033(gi)005:355: tshul bzhin du bya dgos so //
NK033(gi)005:356: dgu pa sngags kyi byin gyis brlab pa yin pas lus bde lugs su bag phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:357: sems gzhan du ma yengs par dmigs pa 'di rnams rtse gcig bsgom par zhu /
NK033(gi)005:358: spyi bo'i steng du 'khor lo ni //
NK033(gi)005:359: gser las grub pa'i rtsibs brgyad pa //
NK033(gi)005:360: yi ge +amo gyis mtshan par bsgom //
NK033(gi)005:361: lce yi steng du pad+ma ni //
NK033(gi)005:364: snying gar rdo rje rgya gram ni //
NK033(gi)005:365: mthing ga'i lte ba h'u gis brgyan //
NK033(gi)005:366: ces pa rnams shin tu gsal ba la sems gtod la 'bru gsum brjod par bya /
NK033(gi)005:369: de la sems zin pa dang /
NK033(gi)005:370: de ni rgyu ma ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)005:371: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags bstan pa yin pas dmigs pa 'di ltar mdzod /
NK033(gi)005:372: spyi gtsug d+h+au ti'i nang na mar //
NK033(gi)005:373: yi ge ham ni mgo mthur 'phyang //
NK033(gi)005:374: dkar la 'tsher ba bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)005:375: lte ba'i nang du a dmar po //
NK033(gi)005:376: dus mtha'i me bzhin dmar ba la //
NK033(gi)005:377: me mar bzhin du 'bar ba las //
NK033(gi)005:378: spyi bo'i ham las bdud rtsi bab //
NK033(gi)005:379: rang lus bdud rtsis khengs par bsam pa la shes pa rtse gcig tu gtod cig /
NK033(gi)005:380: d+aa dril sogs rol mo bsgrag /
NK033(gi)005:381: a ham zhes mang du brjod /
NK033(gi)005:382: bzlas brjod las kyi sngags bstan pa yin pas dmigs pa 'di ltar sgoms shig /
NK033(gi)005:385: d+aa ki ma ni gsum du gyur //
NK033(gi)005:386: bud med dmar mo gzhon sha can //
NK033(gi)005:387: gcer bu rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)005:388: skra grol ba ti'i sham thabs can //
NK033(gi)005:389: d+aa ma ru dang kha t+w+aam ga /
NK033(gi)005:391: lo brgyad pa yin tshod la //
NK033(gi)005:392: gar ni khyug khyug mdzad par sgoms la ma yengs shig /
NK033(gi)005:395: rol mo'i sgra drag tu byas la /
NK033(gi)005:396: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta a bi pra sa la /
NK033(gi)005:397: zhes sngags mang du brjod pas /
NK033(gi)005:400: sems la bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams skye ba
NK033(gi)005:401: ste byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags gsum 'byung bar gsungs
NK033(gi)005:402: so // bcu pa ye shes dbab pa'i rgyun sgo
NK033(gi)005:403: gsum la brtan par bya ba'i phyir byin rlabs rnam
NK033(gi)005:404: gsum bya ba la dmigs pa 'di ltar mdzod cig
NK033(gi)005:405: so // / khyod kyi spyi bo'i gtsug tu ni //
NK033(gi)005:406: +amo ni btso ma gser lta bu //
NK033(gi)005:408: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa //
NK033(gi)005:409: lte ba +amo gyis mtshan par bsgom //
NK033(gi)005:410: rdo rje rgya gram spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:411: +amo badz+ra a d+hi pa ti s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK033(gi)005:412: khyod kyi lce yi steng du ni //
NK033(gi)005:416: rgya gram mgrin par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:417: +amo badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)005:418: khyod kyi snying ga'i gnas su ni //
NK033(gi)005:419: h'u sngon rgya gram gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)005:421: lcags kyi rdo rje rgya gram la //
NK033(gi)005:422: lte ba h'u gis mtshan par bsgom //
NK033(gi)005:423: rgya gram snying gar bzhag la sngags gong bzhin brjod /
NK033(gi)005:424: me tog lag tu gtad la /
NK033(gi)005:425: me tog 'di nyid khyod rang gi tshe rabs sngon
NK033(gi)005:426: nas 'brel pa'i rigs gang yin pa'i lha la phog
NK033(gi)005:427: par shog cig snyam pa'i mos 'dun rtse gcig pas
NK033(gi)005:428: 'dor bar zhu / zhes dkyil 'khor ram tshom bu la 'dor du gzhug /
NK033(gi)005:429: de ltar dor ba'i me tog dbus su phog na sangs rgyas rigs /
NK033(gi)005:433: byang du las kyi rigs su nges pa yin pas
NK033(gi)005:434: so so'i rigs kyi he ru ka nyid gtso bor
NK033(gi)005:436: de dag gis 'jug pa'i chos rnams grub /
NK033(gi)005:437: zhugs nas mngon par dbang bskur ba la rtsa ba dbang bzhi /
NK033(gi)005:438: so so'i rjes 'brel bcas 'byung ba las /
NK033(gi)005:439: dang po bum pa'i dbang gi slad du khyed rang
NK033(gi)005:440: dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su phyag rgya lnga yi
NK033(gi)005:441: man+dala gyi steng du 'khod pa la /
NK033(gi)005:442: 'di rnams 'grub na dngos su de ltar bshams /
NK033(gi)005:443: slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha dbyer med pas
NK033(gi)005:444: rin po che'i bum pa ye shes bdud rtsi'i rgyun
NK033(gi)005:445: gyis bkang bas dbang bskur bas rigs lnga ye shes
NK033(gi)005:446: lnga'i dbang chen yongs su rdzogs pa thob par mos
NK033(gi)005:449: dbang bskur 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)005:450: sangs rgyas kun gyi bum pa'i dbang //
NK033(gi)005:451: sangs rgyas kun gyi phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK033(gi)005:452: sangs rgyas kun tu dbang bsgrub phyir //
NK033(gi)005:453: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)005:454: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)005:455: bum pa mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:459: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rigs rnam pa lnga'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:460: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:461: rdo rje'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:462: rin po che'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:463: pad+ma'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:464: las kyi rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:465: slar yang gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:469: pad+ma k+aa la sha h+r+aih karma ka la sha +aah
NK033(gi)005:470: sku rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK033(gi)005:471: / sprul pa sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:472: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:473: chos kyi sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:474: ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:475: gsang ba'i sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:480: pad+ma lo tsa ni h+r+aih karma lo tsa ni +aah
NK033(gi)005:481: ye shes rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK033(gi)005:482: cig / chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:483: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:484: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:485: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:486: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:487: gzung ba rang bzhin med pa sku'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:488: 'dzin pa rang bzhin med pa gsung gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:489: de nyid gang du yang ma grub pa thugs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:490: ces bum dbang bskur la bum pas khrus gsol ba ni /
NK033(gi)005:492: sangs rgyas kun gyis khrus gsol ba //
NK033(gi)005:493: ye shes chu bo khrus kyi rdzing //
NK033(gi)005:494: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK033(gi)005:495: bkra shis bum pa spyi blugs bzang //
NK033(gi)005:496: dbang bskur thams cad 'dir gsol cig /
NK033(gi)005:497: dbang bskur 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)005:498: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK033(gi)005:499: gsang ba gsum las byung ba yi //
NK033(gi)005:500: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin par bya //
NK033(gi)005:501: phung po lnga ni rnam dag cing //
NK033(gi)005:502: nyon mongs lnga ni sbyong bar byed //
NK033(gi)005:503: ye shes lnga yi ngo bo nyid //
NK033(gi)005:504: dpal ldan sku yi dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)005:505: +amo badz+ra a d+hi s+t+wam sat+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK033(gi)005:506: +amo badz+ra a d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)005:507: +amo badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)005:508: zhes khrus byas zhing bum chu blud /
NK033(gi)005:509: gnyis pa gsang dbang gi don du dkyil 'khor gyi
NK033(gi)005:510: lho phyogs su sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i thig le
NK033(gi)005:511: bkod pa'i steng du 'khod pa la /
NK033(gi)005:512: ka p+aa la bdud rtsis bkang bas dbang bskur bas
NK033(gi)005:513: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi dbang chen
NK033(gi)005:514: yongs su rdzogs pa thob par mos shig /
NK033(gi)005:515: ka p+aa la'i bdud rtsi spyi bo sogs gnas gsum du rim par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:516: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK033(gi)005:517: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK033(gi)005:518: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)005:519: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir gsol cig /
NK033(gi)005:521: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK033(gi)005:522: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK033(gi)005:523: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK033(gi)005:524: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK033(gi)005:525: rgyud drug sems can kun bsgral phyir //
NK033(gi)005:526: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi ste //
NK033(gi)005:527: bdud rtsi dam pa'i dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)005:528: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)005:529: rdo rje can gyi +amo bsgom ste //
NK033(gi)005:530: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)005:531: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)005:533: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)005:535: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)005:536: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)005:537: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah lce yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)005:538: rdo rje can gyi h'u bsgom ste //
NK033(gi)005:539: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)005:540: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)005:542: sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:543: gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:544: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:545: de nas ye shes kyibaduda rtsi blud pa ni /
NK033(gi)005:546: rdo rje ka p+aa la'i khar bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)005:548: rdo rje 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)005:549: rdo rje rgyal po rab tu bzang //
NK033(gi)005:550: rdo rje rab tu 'bar ba yis //
NK033(gi)005:551: dag pa'i bdud rtsir byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)005:552: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)005:554: gzhan la smra bar ma byed cig /
NK033(gi)005:555: a la la hoh zhes bdud rtsi lan gsum du sbyin /
NK033(gi)005:556: gsum pa sher dbang bskur ba'i slad du khyed rang
NK033(gi)005:557: dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su byang sems dkar dmar
NK033(gi)005:558: gyi thig le'i man+dala steng du 'khod pa la thabs
NK033(gi)005:559: dang shes rab thig le dkar dmar gyis dbang bskur
NK033(gi)005:560: bas sku gsung thugs bde ba mchog tu mi 'gyur
NK033(gi)005:561: ba'i dbang chen thob par mos shig /
NK033(gi)005:562: me long ril bu bcas spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:564: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK033(gi)005:565: byang sems thig ler rab sbyar nas //
NK033(gi)005:566: dag cing gsal la dri ma med //
NK033(gi)005:567: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK033(gi)005:568: 'di la yang dag ngos bzung med //
NK033(gi)005:569: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)005:570: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)005:571: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)005:577: bam d+ai pa su khi ni /
NK033(gi)005:578: hoh gan+d+he tsit+ta hoh k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)005:579: byang sems thig le dkar po rnam par dag pa
NK033(gi)005:580: ni zla ba shar ba lta bu'i dbang thob par
NK033(gi)005:581: gyur cig / byang sems thig le dmar po rnam
NK033(gi)005:582: par dag pa ni nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i
NK033(gi)005:584: ces brjod la ril bu dkar dmar lce thog tu bzhag /
NK033(gi)005:585: sku bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:586: a la la hoh gsung bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:587: a la la hoh thugs bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:588: a la la hoh zhes byang sems thig le'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)005:589: de dag gi mtha' brten du bcu gcig pa bkra shis tshe'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)005:590: 'khor 'das brtan g.yo'i tshe bcud 'dus pa'i bum pa
NK033(gi)005:591: khyed rang gi spyi bor bzhag cing dbang bskur bas
NK033(gi)005:592: / bum pa las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs /
NK033(gi)005:594: 'chi ba med pa'i tshe dang rdo rje lta bu'i srog thob par sgoms shig /
NK033(gi)005:597: skal ldan dbang mchog lha yi lung //
NK033(gi)005:598: bdud rtsi gang rgya sman gyi lung //
NK033(gi)005:599: rin chen zla gam dbang gi lung //
NK033(gi)005:601: rin chen sna lnga'i bum pa ru //
NK033(gi)005:602: rdo rje tshe yis bkang nas kyang //
NK033(gi)005:603: rin chen rgyan gyis bklubs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)005:604: bu yi spyi bor dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)005:605: bu khyod tshe dbang gnas par shog /
NK033(gi)005:606: +amo b+h+r+aum h'u b+h+r+aum t+r+aam b+h+r+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum +aahb+h+r+aum /
NK033(gi)005:607: na mo dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK033(gi)005:608: rigs kyi bu 'di la rdo rje tshe'i dbang bskur bas /
NK033(gi)005:610: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:611: skye med kyi ye shes su gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:612: 'chi med kyi bdud rtsir gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:613: mi 'gyur ba'i g.yung drung du gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:614: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan du gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:615: mi shigs pa'i rdo rjer gyur cig /
NK033(gi)005:617: bcu gnyis pa zhing khams bstan pa 'di bzhin du nges 'tshal /
NK033(gi)005:619: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)005:620: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)005:621: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)005:622: badz+ra he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)005:623: rdo rje mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)005:624: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)005:625: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:626: lho phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)005:627: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)005:628: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)005:629: rat+na he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)005:630: rin chen mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)005:631: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)005:632: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:633: nub phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)005:634: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)005:635: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)005:636: pad+ma he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)005:638: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)005:639: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:640: byang phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)005:641: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)005:642: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)005:643: karma he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)005:644: las kyi mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)005:645: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)005:646: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:647: dbus phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)005:648: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)005:649: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)005:650: bud+d+ha he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)005:651: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)005:652: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)005:653: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:655: bcu gsum pa lam 'di'i nyams len gyi rtsa ba
NK033(gi)005:656: rdo rje'i tshig rkang tshul bzhi'i sgom shing gtad pa
NK033(gi)005:657: yin pas 'di'i don nges par mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)005:658: tshul shing lag tu gtad la /
NK033(gi)005:660: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK033(gi)005:661: bden pa gnyis la yang dag bsten //
NK033(gi)005:662: de bzhin kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK033(gi)005:663: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:664: sgra dang tshig kun rdzob yin /
NK033(gi)005:666: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK033(gi)005:667: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)005:669: ye shes 'khyil ba rdo rje'i bum //
NK033(gi)005:670: sogs tshul shing gi yi ge nyid tshar gcig bklag /
NK033(gi)005:671: de ltar ye shes kyi tshul /
NK033(gi)005:674: dbyings kyi tshul te rnam pa bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin las nam yang ma g.yos par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)005:675: de nas dbang bzhi pa tshig dbang bskur ba'i slad
NK033(gi)005:676: du khyed rang dkyil 'khor gyi byang phyogs su gur
NK033(gi)005:677: gum gyi chus rdo rje rgya gram bris pa'i steng
NK033(gi)005:678: du 'khod par mos la snyan gtod par zhu /
NK033(gi)005:679: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK033(gi)005:680: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)005:681: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK033(gi)005:682: skyes tsam nyid nas skye ba med //
NK033(gi)005:683: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK033(gi)005:684: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)005:686: skye 'gags med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK033(gi)005:687: skye med kyi ngang du spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)005:688: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)005:689: a ha hoh 'di ltar 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad gang nas kyang ma skyes /
NK033(gi)005:691: gang la'ang gnas pa med pa ste gdod ma nyid
NK033(gi)005:692: nas skye 'gag gnas gsum dang bral ba'i don shes
NK033(gi)005:693: par mdzod la mnyam par zhog cig /
NK033(gi)005:695: de'i mtha' brten du bcu bzhi pa sgom thag gtad
NK033(gi)005:696: pa yin pas 'di dang mi 'bral bar mdzod cig
NK033(gi)005:699: byams dang snying rje'i thugs mnga' zhing //
NK033(gi)005:700: sangs rgyas phrin las bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)005:701: bde ba'i bka' nan 'di bcings nas //
NK033(gi)005:702: chos dang chos nyid bsgom par gyis //
NK033(gi)005:703: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)005:705: bco lnga pa sgom rten 'di la brten nas lus
NK033(gi)005:706: kyi gnad dang ldan pas chos nyid kyi don bsgom
NK033(gi)005:707: par gyis shig / sgom rten lag g.yon du gtad la /
NK033(gi)005:709: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin chos sku'i gdung //
NK033(gi)005:710: chos rje 'od dpag med pa bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)005:711: bde ba'i lus la rab brten nas //
NK033(gi)005:712: chos kyi dbyings nas ma g.yos phyir //
NK033(gi)005:713: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)005:715: de nas dbang bskur thams cad kyi snying po brgyud
NK033(gi)005:716: pa'i bla ma rnams kyi byin rlabs rim par 'jug
NK033(gi)005:717: pa'i ye shes 'pho ba'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK033(gi)005:718: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas rtsa ba brgyud par
NK033(gi)005:719: bcas pa'i thugs rgyud dgongs pa'i byin rlabs ye shes
NK033(gi)005:720: kyi rang bzhin 'od kyi gong bu zhig 'phros nas
NK033(gi)005:721: khyed rang gi snying gar thim par bsam la thugs
NK033(gi)005:722: yid dbyer med du bsres la rang bzhin gyi 'od
NK033(gi)005:723: gsal ba'i ngang du zhog cig /
NK033(gi)005:724: slob dpon bzhengs te phyag spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)005:728: a ni skye med mi rtog brda //
NK033(gi)005:729: ha ni 'gag med gsal ba'i brda //
NK033(gi)005:730: ho ni gnyis su med pa'i brda //
NK033(gi)005:731: 'i ni dbyer mi phyed pa'i brda //
NK033(gi)005:732: spros bral don gyi rnal 'byor te //
NK033(gi)005:733: de kho na nyid kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK033(gi)005:735: 'di dag gi don gsal ba byin rlabs 'bring bsdus las 'byung ba'o //
NK033(gi)005:736: bcu drug pa bka' srung mkha' 'gro ma la las kyi gnyer gtad pa ste /
NK033(gi)005:737: 'bar ba me'i gdong can 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK033(gi)005:738: kyis ji ltar bsgos pa'i phrin las thams cad thogs
NK033(gi)005:739: med du sgrub par zhal gyis bzhes par mos shig
NK033(gi)005:740: / gtor ma lag tu gtad la /
NK033(gi)005:743: zhing las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)005:744: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)005:745: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)005:746: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)005:747: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)005:748: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)005:749: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa ni //
NK033(gi)005:750: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)005:751: mkha' la gshegs ma mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)005:753: las las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)005:754: ming po rdo rjee mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)005:755: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)005:756: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)005:757: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)005:758: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)005:759: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)005:760: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)005:761: mkha' la spyod ma'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)005:763: mngal las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)005:764: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)005:765: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)005:766: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)005:767: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)005:768: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)005:769: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)005:770: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)005:772: slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor ba'i lha rgyal ba sras
NK033(gi)005:773: dang bcas pa rnams kyis bkra shis pa'i bden tshig
NK033(gi)005:774: dbyangs su len / me tog man+d+aa ra ba'i char
NK033(gi)005:775: sil mar bsnyil bas dbang gi ye shes ma skyes
NK033(gi)005:776: dbyangs su len / pa skyes / skyes pa gong
NK033(gi)005:777: nas gong du 'phel ba sogs dge legs rtag pa
NK033(gi)005:778: dam pa'i snang ba rab tu spel bar mos shig
NK033(gi)005:779: dbyangs su len / pa skyes / / zhal nas
NK033(gi)005:780: gsungs pa'i tshigs su bcad pas thog drangs shis brjod
NK033(gi)005:781: rgyas par spel zhing me tog 'thor /
NK033(gi)005:782: gsum pa rjes kyi bya ba la /
NK033(gi)005:784: de dag rnams kyis theg pa rim pa dgu'i mthar
NK033(gi)005:785: thug bla na med pa a ti rdzogs pa chen
NK033(gi)005:786: po sde gsum las nang skor klong sde'i smin byed
NK033(gi)005:787: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i sgom tshul bla ma'i
NK033(gi)005:788: byin rlabs kyi cho ga rgyas pa'i rim pa tshul
NK033(gi)005:789: bzhin grub pa lags pas thun mong dang thun mong
NK033(gi)005:790: ma yin pa'i dam tshig mtha' dag tshul bzhin bsrung
NK033(gi)005:792: gtso bos ji ltar sogs gsum /
NK033(gi)005:795: dge bsngo byas la slob ma rnams gyes /
NK033(gi)005:796: slob dpon gyi dkyil 'khor gyi rjes chog gtor ma btang ba nas /
NK033(gi)005:797: bsdu ldang bsngo smon gyi bar phrin las su ji skad bshad pa ltar bya'o //
NK033(gi)005:798: gdos bcas 'od kyi sku ru grol byed pa //
NK033(gi)005:799: dpal seng thugs bcud rnam snang lo ts+aa bas //
NK033(gi)005:800: dka' dgus btsal ba'i zab chos 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)005:801: u dum ra'i dper mtshungs dkon pa'i phul //
NK033(gi)005:802: gang 'di'i nyams len tshul bzhin bgyid nus pa'i //
NK033(gi)005:803: skal bzang skye bo rgyun mi chad 'byon nas //
NK033(gi)005:804: lus can bye ba rdul snyed gzhi dbyings su //
NK033(gi)005:805: rnam grol phrin las dbyar mtsho ltar rgyas shog /
NK033(gi)005:806: 'di la 'dzing badz+ra pra b+has tshigs bcad du bsdebs
NK033(gi)005:807: pa nyid las gsal byed kyi yig cha gzhan ma
NK033(gi)005:808: bzhugs / yig rnying de'ang rtsa tho lta bur bsdus
NK033(gi)005:809: shing mchan bu'i dpe rgyun ma dag pa mang ba
NK033(gi)005:810: dang deng dus tshul 'di 'dra go don phyag len
NK033(gi)005:811: zhun thar gcod mkhan med pa'i dpe mthong bon gyer
NK033(gi)005:812: bzhugs / mang bas / zab chos kyi rgyud la
NK033(gi)005:813: phan par re ba'i lhag pa'i bsam pas a ti'i
NK033(gi)005:814: rnal 'byor tsam po pa pad+ma gar dbang blo gros
NK033(gi)005:815: mtha' yas pa'i sdes rdzong shod bde gshegs 'dus pa'i
